{{Other uses|Treaty of Stralsund (disambiguation){{!}}Treaty of Stralsund}}
The '''Treaty of Stralsund''', arranged on 12 February 1354, settled border disputes resulting from the [[Pomerania during the Late Middle Ages|wars for Rugian succession]] between the duchies of [[Mecklenburg]] and [[Duchy of Pomerania|Pomerania]].

